{"tid":2006312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[東網] 傳粵港澳互認檢測　在港隔離後入境廣東免檢疫","createTime":"2020-05-07T16:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T16:47:03.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75b2a9d4c36711553a64f12bda4bb13887c5498e","tid":2006312,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"[東網] 傳粵港澳互認檢測 在港隔離後入境廣東免檢疫<br />\n05月07日(四) 17:34<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府日前宣布豁免在內地設廠的港商及員工14日的強制檢疫，惟港商入境內地仍要隔離14天。然而網上近日流傳一份文件顯示，廣東省已採取粵港澳三地隔離醫學觀察結果互認措施，港澳人員只要滿足一定條件，可免除再隔離。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n[url<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200508/00176_011.html[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200508%2F00176_011.html%5B%2Furl%5D&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0DbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=3e291766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200508/00176_011.html[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"a4624b963e5bee5cdf542b7407df8cbf0b4f3ba0","tid":2006312,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"今晚12點前我要見到十萬訂閱抵制tvb民間自發gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005108</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}